name: All of You Fascists Bound to Lose
comments: Recorded in New York by Decca Records for Alan Lomax's radio ballad opera The Martins and The Coys. Alan Lomax shopped this around but no stations were interested, eventually it was sold the BBC. First aired in the UK on June 26, 1944 on BBC Radio Home Service Re-aired on August 17, 1944 on BBC Radio.
